             what-we-diverge : structurally identical · this is "do what rustc does"
    PA.02 · cargo build-cache · what-we-take : per-module fingerprint · re-build only changed modules ·
             what-we-diverge : CSSL has its own module hash (content + dep-closure) ¬ Cargo's
